Check for updates without installing

Usage: distronomicon --app <APP> check [OPTIONS] --repo <REPO> --state-directory <STATE_DIRECTORY>

Options:
      --repo <REPO>
          GitHub repository (owner/name)
      --state-directory <STATE_DIRECTORY>
          State directory [env: STATE_DIRECTORY=]
      --github-token <TOKEN>
          GitHub API token [env: GITHUB_TOKEN]
      --github-host <HOST>
          GitHub API host [env: GITHUB_HOST=] [default: api.github.com]
      --allow-prerelease
          Allow prerelease versions
  -h, --help
          Print help
